  dsimp [Œ¥, œÉ, fin.succ_above, fin.pred_above],
  rcases i with ‚ü®i, _‚ü©,
  rcases j with ‚ü®j, _‚ü©,
  rcases k with ‚ü®k, _‚ü©,
  simp only [subtype.mk_lt_mk, fin.cast_succ_mk] at H,
